      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Jan Renze Steenhuisen</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/renze-steenhuisen-448b42b/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/8/84/RenzeSteenhuisen.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:RenzeSteenhuisen.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Renze Steenhuisen <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Jan Renze Steenhuisen</b>,<br />\na Dutch senior software engineer and computer scientist with interests in computer chess, computer games, and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Multi-agent_planning\">multi-agent planning</a>.\nHe holds M.Sc. and Ph.D. degrees from <a href=\"/Delft_University_of_Technology\" title=\"Delft University of Technology\">TU Delft</a> in 2005 and 2013 respectively.\nHis 2005 Master's thesis was about <a href=\"/Parallel_Search\" title=\"Parallel Search\">Parallel Search</a>, the design and implementation of a parallel two-player state space searcher called <a href=\"/index.php?title=DarkSight&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"DarkSight (page does not exist)\">DarkSight</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, performing <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Transposition-driven_scheduling\">Transposition-driven scheduling</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2003\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2003</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2004\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2004</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2005\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jan_Renze_Steenhuisen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jan Renze Steenhuisen</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i>Report on the 10th Advances in Computer Games Conference</i>.  <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#26_4\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 26, No. 4</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Games_10\" title=\"Advances in Computer Games 10\">Advances in Computer Games 10</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jan Renze Steenhuisen</a> (<b>2005</b>). <i>New Results in Deep-Search Behaviour</i>.  <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#28_4\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 28, No. 4</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://citeseerx.ist.psu.edu/viewdoc/summary?doi=10.1.1.104.9527\">CiteSeerX</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jan Renze Steenhuisen</a> (<b>2005</b>). <i>Transposition-Driven Scheduling in Parallel Two-Player State-Space Search</i>. Master's thesis, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://citeseerx.ist.psu.edu/viewdoc/summary?doi=10.1.1.96.174\">CiteSeerX</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jan Renze Steenhuisen</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/w/Witteveen:Cees\">Cees Witteveen</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/z/Zhang:Yingqian\">Yingqian Zhan</a> (<b>2007</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-88833-8_1\">Plan-Coordination Mechanisms and the Price of Autonomy</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/clima/clima2007.html\">CLIMA VIII</a>, Invited Paper</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jan Renze Steenhuisen</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/w/Witteveen:Cees\">Cees Witteveen</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://content.iospress.com/articles/multiagent-and-grid-systems/mgs00138\">Plan decoupling of agents with qualitatively constrained task</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.iospress.nl/journal/multiagent-and-grid-systems/\">Multiagent and Grid Systems</a>, Vol. 5, No. 4</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jan Renze Steenhuisen</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i>Coordinated Multi-Agent Planning and Scheduling</i>. Ph.D. thesis, <a href=\"/Delft_University_of_Technology\" title=\"Delft University of Technology\">TU Delft</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jan_Renze_Steenhuisen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2003\">2003</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jan_Renze_Steenhuisen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2003\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=323898\">Making positions in eps</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Renze Steenhuisen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 27, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Chess_Position\" title=\"Chess Position\">Chess Position</a>, <a href=\"/Forsyth-Edwards_Notation#FEN2EPS\" title=\"Forsyth-Edwards Notation\">Fen2eps</a> </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=325977\">Search algorithms</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Renze Steenhuisen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 06, 2003</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2004\">2004</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jan_Renze_Steenhuisen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2004\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=348097\">Determining location of LSB/MSB</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Renze Steenhuisen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 09, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/BitScan\" title=\"BitScan\">BitScan</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=354812\">History Heuristic</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Renze Steenhuisen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 16, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/History_Heuristic\" title=\"History Heuristic\">History Heuristic</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=357382\">SEE and FH-%</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Renze Steenhuisen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 30, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Static_Exchange_Evaluation\" title=\"Static Exchange Evaluation\">SEE</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=358297\">Move ordering at root</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Renze Steenhuisen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 04, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Move_Ordering\" title=\"Move Ordering\">Move Ordering</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=358836\">Hashkey collisions (typical numbers)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Renze Steenhuisen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 07, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table#Collisions\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table - Collisions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=376529\">Question about Crafty and Bishop Pair</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Renze Steenhuisen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 13, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Bishop_Pair\" title=\"Bishop Pair\">Bishop Pair</a>, <a href=\"/Crafty\" title=\"Crafty\">Crafty</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=388362\">Single Reply Extension</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Renze Steenhuisen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 20, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/One_Reply_Extensions\" title=\"One Reply Extensions\">One Reply Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=398421\">Repetition Detection</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Renze Steenhuisen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 01, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Repetitions\" title=\"Repetitions\">Repetitions</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005\">2005</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jan_Renze_Steenhuisen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2005\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=416677\">Aspiration Window sizes</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Renze Steenhuisen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 14, 2005&#160;» <a href=\"/Aspiration_Windows\" title=\"Aspiration Windows\">Aspiration Windows</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=423308\">Jeremiah's Wall Detection</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Renze Steenhuisen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 28, 2005&#160;» <a href=\"/Blockage_Detection\" title=\"Blockage Detection\">Blockage Detection</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jan_Renze_Steenhuisen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/renze-steenhuisen-448b42b/\">Renze Steenhuisen | LinkedIn</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jan_Renze_Steenhuisen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/renze-steenhuisen-448b42b/\">Renze Steenhuisen | LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jan Renze Steenhuisen</a> (<b>2005</b>). <i>Transposition-Driven Scheduling in Parallel Two-Player State-Space Search</i>. Master's Thesis, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://citeseerx.ist.psu.edu/viewdoc/summary?doi=10.1.1.96.174\">CiteSeerX</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/John_Romein\" title=\"John Romein\">John Romein</a>, <a href=\"/Aske_Plaat\" title=\"Aske Plaat\">Aske Plaat</a>, <a href=\"/Henri_Bal\" title=\"Henri Bal\">Henri Bal</a>, <a href=\"/Jonathan_Schaeffer\" title=\"Jonathan Schaeffer\">Jonathan Schaeffer</a> (<b>1999</b>). <i>Transposition Table Driven Work Scheduling in Distributed Search</i>. <a href=\"/Conferences#AAAI-99\" title=\"Conferences\">AAAI-99</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.aaai.org/Papers/AAAI/1999/AAAI99-103.pdf\">pdf</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/John_Romein\" title=\"John Romein\">John Romein</a>, <a href=\"/Henri_Bal\" title=\"Henri Bal\">Henri Bal</a>, <a href=\"/Jonathan_Schaeffer\" title=\"Jonathan Schaeffer\">Jonathan Schaeffer</a>, <a href=\"/Aske_Plaat\" title=\"Aske Plaat\">Aske Plaat</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i>A Performance Analysis of Transposition-Table-Driven Scheduling in Distributed Search</i>. <a href=\"/IEEE#TPDS\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE Transactions on Parallel and Distributed Systems</a>, Vol. 13, No. 5, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.vu.nl/~bal/Papers/tds.pdf\">pdf</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/s/Steenhuisen:J=_Renze\">dblp: J. Renze Steenhuisen</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301114325\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.017 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.018 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 101/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 210/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:5875-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301114325 and revision id 13320\n -->\n"
